frames.caption: A couple sits on a blanket in a grassy field, gazing at a star-filled sky with a prominent Milky Way. The scene is set against a backdrop of mountains and a serene landscape.
frames.description: The scene depicts a romantic and tranquil night setting where a couple enjoys stargazing. They are seated on a blanket in a lush, grassy area with a clear view of the night sky, which is filled with stars and constellations. A mountain range is visible in the distance, enhancing the peaceful atmosphere.
